data.description: Like BRAND NEW 2021 model doublewide home with 3 bedroom 2 bath AND FURNISHED!This home located in the Shallotte Pointe area and is in close proximity to all shops, restaurants and area beaches. This home is like new and offers an amazing kitchen layout with a pantry, generous sized master bedroom with a walk in closet & master bathroom. The guest rooms are also nicely sized with walk in closets as well.Do not miss out on this opportunity!
